        <argsstring></argsstring>
        <name>MR_VertCoordsDiff</name>
        <briefdescription>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>this object stores a difference between two vectors with 3D coordinates</para>
<para>if the vectors are similar then this object is small, if the vectors are very distinct then this object will be even larger than one vector itself Generated from class <computeroutput>MR::VertCoordsDiff</computeroutput>. Supported <computeroutput><ref refid="common_8h_1ac983b89bddb9b22c9b416f31399f0095" kindref="member">MR_PassBy</ref></computeroutput> modes: <computeroutput>MR_PassBy_DefaultConstruct</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>MR_PassBy_Copy</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>MR_PassBy_Move</computeroutput> (and <computeroutput>MR_PassBy_DefaultArgument</computeroutput> and <computeroutput>MR_PassBy_NoObject</computeroutput> if supported by the callee). </para>
        </detaileddescription>
